							<div id="switch" class="doc-switch doc-section">
								<header class="header">
									<h2 class="title">Switch</h2>
								</header>
								<div class="content">
									<div class="subsection">
										<h3 class="title">Basic Usage</h3>
										<p>Switch allows you to create a group of switchable options. Switched option will unswitch other options on the same group. Use <code>.switch</code> on <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> to create a switch link, which will switch element from <code>href</code>. Lastly, group all switch elements with <code>data-switch-group</code>.</p>
										<div class="example">
											<div class="doc-switch-nav">
												<a href="#switch-1" class="js-switch is-switched" data-switch-group="switch">Switch 1</a>
												<a href="#switch-2" class="js-switch" data-switch-group="switch">Switch 2</a>
												<a href="#switch-3" class="js-switch" data-switch-group="switch">Switch 3</a>
											</div>
											<div class="doc-switch-content">
												<div id="switch-1" class="js-switch-target is-switched" data-switch-group="switch">
													<p>Switch 1</p>
												</div>
												<div id="switch-2" class="js-switch-target" data-switch-group="switch">
													<p>Switch 2</p>
												</div>
												<div id="switch-3" class="js-switch-target" data-switch-group="switch">
													<p>Switch 3</p>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>

									<div class="subsection">
										<h3 class="title">Advance Usage</h3>
										<p>Below listed all options for switch</p>
										<ul>
											<li><code>data-switch-group="[name]"</code> -> group switch elements (required)</li>
											<li><code>data-switch-method="auto|manual"</code> -> how switch is handled, default is auto</li>
											<li><code>data-switch-duration="[second]"</code> -> how long is switch animation if switch method is auto</li>
											<li><code>data-switch-scroll="[selector]"</code> -> switch scroll to</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

