									</div>

									<div class="subsection">
										<h3 class="title">Alternate Usage</h3>
										<p>Toggle can be triggered with hover by adding <code>.toggle-hover</code> on <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>.</p>
										<div class="example">
											<a href="#toggle-hover-test" class="js-toggle js-toggle-hover">Toggle Them!</a>
											<div id="toggle-hover-test" class="doc-toggle-test">
