											</div>
										</div>
									</div>

									<div class="subsection">
										<h3 class="title">Advance Usage</h3>
										<p>Below listed all options for toggle</p>
										<ul>
											<li><code>data-toggle-target="[selector]"</code> -> define toggle target if href is not used</li>
											<li><code>data-toggle-area="[selector]"</code> -> toggle will end if mouse click outside this area or leave this area</li>
											<li><code>data-toggle-method="auto|manual"</code> -> how toggle is handled, default is auto</li>
											<li><code>data-toggle-duration="[second]"</code> -> how long is toggle animation if toggle method is auto</li>
											<li><code>data-toggle-scroll="[selector]"</code> -> toggle scroll to</li>
											<li><code>data-toggle-focus="[selector]"</code> -> toggle will focus on targeted form</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
